FT  15 NOV 94 / Bathers paralysed by mystery virus
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
An investigation is being launched into the cause of a suspected virus that
partly paralysed bathers at two popular tourist beaches.
Two teenagers are confined to wheelchairs after contracting the virus, which
attacks the nervous system. Both lost the use of their legs within hours of
